What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Refrigerated ISO Containers Market?

Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Refrigerated ISO Containers Market

The refrigerated ISO containers market is expected to witness market growth at a rate of approximately 7.5% in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028, and will reach the value of USD 25,000 million by 2028. Data Bridge Market Research report on refrigerated ISO containers market provides analysis and insights regarding the various factors expected to be prevalent throughout the forecast period while providing their impacts on the market’s growth. The rise in the shipping sector globally is escalating the growth of refrigerated ISO containers market.

ISO containers refer to the international intermodal containers that are manufactured in accordance to the specifications outlined by the International Organization for Standardization (ISO). These containers are specifically designed for ship, rail and truck and the design includes the required size, quality of steel and the allowed gross weight. These can be classified according to types such as refrigerated (reefer) container, open top container, flat rack container, dry containers and open top container among others.

The increase in adoption of shipping containers in the seaborne trade across the globe acts as one of the major factors driving the growth of refrigerated ISO containers market. The substantial demand for reefer containers, and favourable government regulations pertaining to emissions coupled with increase in need of standardization of containers, and use of eco-friendly refrigerants in shipping containers accelerate the market growth. The rise in the preference for high cube containers owning to their numerous advantages, and huge demand for marine reefer containers to transport the vaccine as well further influence the market. Additionally, expansion of packaging sector, urbanization, growing containerization and increase in number of international trades positively affect the refrigerated ISO containers market. Furthermore, increase in application of remote container management solutions extend profitable opportunities to the market players in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028.

On the other hand, fluctuations in raw material prices are expected to obstruct the market growth. The decline in demand of the product because of trade conflicts between major countries is projected to challenge the refrigerated ISO containers market in the forecast period of 2021-2028.

